high_descs: Turn left and go forward to the shelves, then look down.
Pick up the black rag from the floor.
Look up to the shelves.
Put the black rag on the bottom shelf.
Look back down to the floor.
Pick up the yellow rag on the floor.
Look up to the shelves.
Put the yellow rag on the bottom shelf, on top of the black rag.
anns.task_desc: Put two rags on the shelf.

high_descs: Turn to your left and go straight to the cabinet.
Bend over and Pick up the black cloth that is on the floor.
With the cloth in hand stand up and  face the cabinet that is in front of you.
place the cloth on the second shelf of the cabinet.
Bend down so you are looking at the cloths on the floor in front of you
Bend down and pick up the white cloth that is on the floor in front of you.
With the white cloth in hand stand up straight and face forward.
Place the white cloth on top of the black cloth on the second shelf in front of you.
anns.task_desc: Pick up two cloths on the floor and place on cabinet.

high_descs: Turn to your left walk forward then face down
Pick up the black cloth on the floor
Raise your body facing the shelf above the floor
Put the black cloth on the shelf in front of you
Look at the yellow cloth on the floor
Pick up the yellow cloth on the floor
Look to the shelf
Put the yellow cloth on top of the black cloth
anns.task_desc: Put black and yellow cloth on the top shelf
